{"tid":432573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日流鼻血，乾燥季節特別嚴重？","createTime":"2017-10-11T15:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T23:41:46.000Z","uid":112849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f8860178675518f5cdd5f17c50e7662745d9e1ac","tid":432573,"uid":112849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:44:15.000Z","msg":"細細個就成日流鼻血 試過細個抱住膝頭哥 唔覺意鬆手撞左落個鼻 咁就流鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個果陣俾屋企人點 話抬高頭就得架喇<br />\n大個先發現其實應該低頭先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近幾年仲嚴重 一到秋天乾啲果陣<br />\n最高峰一日流三次 每次5分鐘起<br />\n已經唔敢撩佢 都自己流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來直頭咩都唔做 低頭由佢滴 試過滴左大概十五分鐘先停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流到尾只要咳左舊血塊出黎就唔再流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣受流鼻血既問題而困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfa2cc0897bd26186f8ccb20a70e48fdda0f8ce","tid":432573,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"可能鼻壁薄血管脹左出黎 睇耳鼻喉科啦"},{"pid":"274d67f7f95a57049167aab11da948a1dd504a42","tid":432573,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"細個都係咁 血塊i know<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中二三開始無"},{"pid":"5f5b4772becba85515714ceb54c4b02ecc1939f4","tid":432573,"uid":138962,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"我都系喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：今晚流左2次 無啦啦自己滴落黎 流左3分鐘就無流了"},{"pid":"d84994cb39a2a6a93da5c0a2313fdf534d0569a1","tid":432573,"uid":134175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"我今日都留左一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb8e7e48d9ef93bd4fe631